hile the Chaos Claws can be used to break through enemy defenses and deliver powerful attacks. The story mode in Lords of Shadow 2 has been stated to be far longer than the previous one. The game is mainly an open world allowing the player to choose what route to take. This game also features a movable camera, something that was not available in the first Lords of Shadow game.", "themes": [{"id": 1, "name": "Action"}, {"id": 17, "name": "Fantasy"}, {"id": 19, "name": "Horror"}, {"id": 38, "name": "Open world"}], "url": "https://www.igdb.com/games/castlevania-lords-of-shadow-2", "videos": [{"id": 814, "name": "Trailer", "video_id": "sXyblWhsDys", "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sXyblWhsDys", "title": "[Official] Castlevania: Lords of Shadow 2 E3 2012 Trailer [HD]", "thumb": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi/sXyblWhsDys/maxresdefault.jpg"}, {"id": 72333, "name": "Trailer", "video_id": "lrBiyEWc3GA", "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lrBiyEWc3GA", "title": "[Official] Dracula's Destiny Trailer HD [Castlevania: Lords of Shadow 2]", "thumb": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi/lrBiyEWc3GA/maxresdefault.jpg"}, {"id": 120009, "name": "Trailer", "video_id": "4ZtF4PqaLvw", "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4ZtF4PqaLvw", "title": "Castlevania Lords of Shadow 2 Trailer (E3 2013)", "thumb": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi/4ZtF4PqaLvw/sddefault.jpg"}, {"id": 120010, "name": "Trailer", "video_id": "12d8yP4f5F4", "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=12d8yP4f5F4", "title": "Mega64: CASTLEVANIA LORDS OF SHADOW 2 TRAILER (E3 2013)", "thumb": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi/12d8yP4f5F4/maxresdefault.jpg"}, {"id": 141724, "name": "VGA 2012 Trailer", "video_id": "MqD0KpEtWwA", "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MqD0KpEtWwA", "title": "Castlevania: Lords of Shadow 2 (VGA 2012 Trailer)", "thumb": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi/MqD0KpEtWwA/maxresdefault.jpg"}], "collections": [{"id": 2491, "name": "Castlevania: Lords of Shadow"}], "characters": [{"id": 2482, "name": "Zobek"}, {"id": 2492, "name": "Cleric"}